title: Delicious Emily: 10 in 1
description:
=============================================================================
ALL EPISODES FROM THE BEGINNING TO THE END! Including all the latest updates!
=============================================================================


Delicious Deluxe (1)
Join Emily on her quest to build a restaurant and make her dreams come true.

Delicious 1.5- Winter edition
Play the exciting Snowtally Awesome sequel to Delicious Deluxe!

Delicious 2 Deluxe
Help Emily rescue her family's finances and get the restaurant business back on track.

Delicious 3: Emily's Tea Garden
Help Emily cater to a wide variety of customers in this vivid treat for the whole family.

Delicious 4: Emily's Taste of Fame
Help get Emily on the road again by whipping up scrumptious meals for a variety of customers.

Delicious 5: Emily's Holiday Season
Help Emily prepare for her family's holiday party at a cozy little lodge.

Delicious 6: Emily's Childhood Memories
Follow Emily on this touching journey, and reminisce heart warming episodes of her life.

Delicious 7: Emily's True Love Premium Edition
Share in Emily's search for true happiness in this wonderful new chapter in the amazing series.

Delicious 8:Emily's Wonder Wedding Premium Edition
Be Emily's special guest as her big day approaches the exciting newest chapter of the captivating series.

Delicious 9: Emily's Honeymoon Cruise Premium Edition 
Watch as Emily takes a trip of a lifetime with Patrick.
